oconocimiento para lograr el bienestar y la salud.\n\u00bfC\u00f3mo funciona la consulta?\n- Reserva tu sesi\u00f3n por whatsapp +34 676355260.\n- Haremos una entrevista, as\u00ed podr\u00e9 obtener toda la informaci\u00f3n que necesito para poder enviarte la terapia floral (inhalada, t\u00f3pica, de uso interno o mixta) indicada para ti.\n- Valor de la sesi\u00f3n: 20 euros.\nLa energ\u00eda sanadora de las flores est\u00e1 a tu disposici\u00f3n. Esta terapia te ayudar\u00e1 a darte cuenta de que no est\u00e1s solo en el camino hacia tu sanaci\u00f3n.\n\u201cSi pudi\u00e9ramos ver el milagro de una sola flor claramente, nuestra vida entera cambiar\u00eda\u201d Buda", "language": null, "image": "https://www.mundoveda.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/mundoveda-sanar-con-flores.jpg", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["#", "http://facebook.com/mundoveda/", "https://plus.google.com/u/0/102141259423648902422", "http://instagram.com/mundoveda/", "http://twitter.com/mundoveda/", "http://youtube.com/channel/UCxu4sDwA86ORuop38EG7AZA/", "https://www.linkedin.com/in/fernanda-montoya-rincon/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/contacto/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/", "javascript:void(0)", "https://www.mundoveda.com", "https://www.mundoveda.com/about/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/tarot/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/que-es-ayurveda/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/que-es-ayurveda-2/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/objetivo-del-ayurveda/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/utilidad/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/pensamiento-ayurvedico/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/un-poco-de-filosofia/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/yoga/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/que-es-el-yoga/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/beneficios-de-practicar-yoga/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/yoga-nidra/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/sanacion-a-traves-del-yoga-nidra/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/consulta-de-salud-ayurveda/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/consulta-de-salud-ayurveda-2/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/tarot/", "https://www.mundoveda.com/t